univention-base-files (3.0.3-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Update/review UCR variable descriptions (Bug #30943)
      Remove UCR variable description for domain/domainname for now, see #32506
      Remove UCR variable description for interfaces/.*/hosts, unused
      Remove UCR variable description for kernel/clobber_modules, kernel/do_bootfloppy,
        kernel/do_initrd, kernel/ramdisk and kernel/silent_loader; no longer used, 
        see Bug 32509
      Revamp category settings
      Remove UCR variable descriptions for lilo/*, removed in UCS 3.0
      Remove UCR variable description for ldap/binaryattributes, causes more 
        confusion than being useful.
      Remove UCR variable descriptions for proxy/password and proxy/username,
        see Bug #18397
      Mark server/role as ReadOnly
      Remove UCR variable description for version/security-patchlevel, no longer
        used since UCS 3.0
      Mark version/version, version/patchlevel, version/releasename and version/erratalevel
	as ReadOnly, they are set automatically during the updates
      Remove UCR variable descriptions for installer/device/.*/fs, installer/device/.*/mp,
	and installer/device/.*/name; only used during installation, see #32527

